sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh<br/>(gRPC Client)
    participant Puller as model-serving-puller<br/>8084/TCP gRPC
    participant Cloud as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(Triton/OVMS/MLServer/TorchServe)

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 1: Model Loading (Puller + Adapter)

    MM->>Puller: LoadModel(modelId, modelPath, modelType)<br/>gRPC plaintext :8084
    Note over Puller: Read storage credentials<br/>from /storage-config Secret

    Puller->>Cloud: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS :443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Cloud provider credentials
    Cloud-->>Puller: Model artifacts<br/>(to /models/_anon_models/{path})

    Note over Puller: Verify & prepare<br/>model directory

    Puller->>Adapter: LoadModel(modelId, modelPath)<br/>gRPC plaintext :8085

    alt Triton Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelLoad(modelName)<br/>gRPC plaintext :8001
        Note over Adapter: Generate config.pbtxt<br/>Adapt model layout<br/>Convert Keras→TF (if .h5)
    else OVMS Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: POST /v1/config/reload<br/>HTTP plaintext :8001
        Note over Adapter: Update model_config_list.json<br/>Batch reload requests<br/>(100ms-3s window)
    else MLServer Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelLoad(modelName)<br/>gRPC plaintext :8001
        Note over Adapter: Generate model-settings.json<br/>Map model type to<br/>implementation class
    else TorchServe Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: RegisterModel(modelName, url)<br/>gRPC plaintext :7071
        Note over Adapter: Generate mmconfig.properties<br/>Configure batch size/delay
    end

    Runtime-->>Adapter: Load success/failure
    Adapter-->>Puller: LoadModel response
    Puller-->>MM: LoadModel response<br/>(model size, max concurrency)

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Loading (Embedded Puller)

    MM->>Adapter: LoadModel(modelId, modelPath, modelType)<br/>gRPC plaintext :8085
    Note over Adapter: Embedded puller reads<br/>/storage-config credentials
    Adapter->>Cloud: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS :443 TLS 1.2+
    Cloud-->>Adapter: Model artifacts
    Adapter->>Runtime: Load model (runtime-specific protocol)
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Load success/failure
    Adapter-->>MM: LoadModel response

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 3: Runtime Status Check

    MM->>Adapter: RuntimeStatus()<br/>gRPC plaintext :8085
    alt TorchServe
        Adapter->>Runtime: Ping()<br/>gRPC plaintext :7070 (inference port)
    else Triton / MLServer
        Adapter->>Runtime: ServerReady()<br/>gRPC plaintext :8001
    else OVMS
        Adapter->>Runtime: GET /v1/config<br/>HTTP plaintext :8001
    end
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Status response
    Adapter-->>MM: RuntimeStatus response<br/>(capacity, max loading concurrency)
